OL,4,CGovernment decision to cut aid budget
OL,5,C'unlawful'
OL,6, The government's decision to cut
OL,7, foreign aid without passing new
OL,8, legislation has been called unlawful by
OL,9, an ex-director of public prosecutions.
OL,11,FLord Macdonald of River Glaven said No
OL,12,F10 acted outside the law when it
OL,13,Fditched its policy of spending 0.7% of
OL,14,Fnational income on aid.
OL,16,FHis formal legal opinion was
OL,17,Fcommissioned by senior Tory MPs
OL,18,Fcampaigning to reverse the aid cut.
OL,20,FThe advice says No 10's decision could
OL,21,Fbe tested in court via judicial review.
